
                    geant4-00-01-ref-12
                    ===================

geant4-00-01-ref-12 is geant4-00-01-ref-11 plus:

persistency-V00-01-06     - Fix for RW->G4RW changes
                          - Fix of GNUmakefile for dependency handling
                          - Fixes for circular dependencies
                          - More bug fixes
PersistentEx01-V00-01-01  - Standalone application "readDB".  See the
                            README files.
config-V00-01-12          - Recent changes for persistency and the fix to
                            liblist.c
vis-V00-01-09             - Bug fix for G4Trap in G4FRSceneFunc
intercoms-V00-01-02       - Headers for SRM
config-V00-01-13          - Added ISO-ANSI setup for DEC, activated if native
                            STL is used.
global-V00-01-11          - Implementaion of ISO-ANSI migration for global.
                          - Virtual destructors in STL interface.
persistency-V00-01-07     - more bug fixes
                          - Use Geant4 schema name space (required by HepODBMS)
                          - Introduced G4PersistencyMessenger and digits
PersistentEx01-V00-01-02  - use interactive and batch mode
                          - bug fix in PersEx01EventAction
                          - updated README, PersistentEx01.in/out
                          - GNUmakefile fix in readDB
greps-V00-01-01           - Headers for SRM
geometry-V00-01-02        - Added initialisation to Eside "side" variable in
                            DistanceToOut(p,v) in CSG solids.
                          - Added a check in G4Trap Makeplane.
                          - Calculate extent of DisplacedSolid
                            corrected plus additional tests for these
                            methods added to all Boolean tests.
global-V00-01-12          - STLInterface: changes for ISO/ANSI C++ support.
                          - Header file comments for SRM.
